            Start Free Demo
        </a>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">AI-Powered Analysis</h3>
            <p>Our advanced algorithms detect security vulnerabilities, performance issues, and code smells in real-time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Instant Feedback</h3>
            <p>Get immediate suggestions for improvement with detailed explanations and code examples.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">GitHub Integration</h3>
            <p>Seamlessly connect with GitHub for one-click code reviews and automated pull request analysis.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="steps">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold">Connect GitHub</h3>
                <p>Securely authenticate with your GitHub account using OAuth</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold">Select Repository</h3>
                <p>Choose any public repository for instant code analysis</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold">Review Results</h3>
                <p>Explore detailed findings with severity ratings and fix suggestions</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 CodeReviewPro. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-2">Security | Terms | Privacy</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>